                <p>Steam sales are always a great opportunity to pick up some bargains, and the recent <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/gallery/best-steam-winter-sale-2025-game-deals/2900-7360/" data-ref-id="2900-7360">Steam Winter Sale</a>, which ran from December 18, 2025 until January 5, 2026, was no exception. While many games typically see a spike in sales and players during these periods, one multiplayer game saw a particularly huge surge in sales following an enormous discount.</p><p><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/games/icarus/" data-ref-id="5000-513911">Icarus</a>, a PvE survival game from New Zealand studio RocketWerkz that was first released in December 2021, was reduced from its usual $35 price to a mere $3.50 during the Steam Winter Sale - an enormous 90% saving.</p>



    
